text: Q Class or Class Q may refer to: == Locomotives == * GNRI Class Q, a Great Northern Railway of Ireland locomotive class * NZR Q class (1878), a New Zealand Railways locomotive class * NZR Q class (1901), a New Zealand Railways locomotive class * SR Class Q, a British Southern Railway locomotive class * WAGR Q class (diesel) ==Other uses== * Library of Congress Classification:Class Q -- Science * Q-class destroyer, a class of warships used by the Royal Navy, Royal Netherlands Navy, and Royal Australian Navy * Classical Quarterly, abbreviated Class. Q.
